      <h2 class="text1">Welcome!</h2>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Enjoy breakfast and lunch at a local favorite. Serving breakfast and lunch, Erv's offers a great way to keep your day moving.</p>
        <p>Please feel free to give us a call with any menu ideas or questions you may have at (260) 420-3729. We're happy to receive any suggestions you have for new specials!</p>
        <p><strong>Today is <%= Time.now.strftime("%A the") %> <%= Time.now.strftime("%e").to_i.ordinalize %>. We are <%= hours_helper %>.</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
